                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9852" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MIS-0290</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">979 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智鉴真伪，“玉”见未来——云南本达黄龙玉的区块链防伪溯源革新之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Intelligent Authentication, Shaping a Bright Future for Jade: Blockchain-Driven Innovation in Anti-Counterfeiting and Traceability for Yunnan Benda Huanglong Jade</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈琦，孟德全，王军栋，胡祥培，张源凯</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南本达黄龙玉文化传媒有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">区块链；黄龙玉；信任；防伪；溯源；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Blockchain; Huanglong Jade; Trust; Anti-counterfeiting; Traceability</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例讲述了云南本达黄龙玉文化传播有限公司杨总如何通过校企合作将区块链引入到黄龙玉的生产、加工以及售卖过程中，进而解决黄龙玉市场面临的信任危机的过程。杨总与胡教授团队以基于区块链的数字证书生成方法为核心，通过“溯源信息记录-来源企业认证-证书实物相对应”的完整逻辑链条实现了黄龙玉商品的“溯源”、“保真”。此外，杨总与胡教授团队合力开发了一套基于区块链的黄龙玉防伪溯源系统，将上述方法在黄龙玉商品上进行了精准实践，实现了区块链技术的应用落地，为建立安全可靠低成本的玉石工业品质量溯源与来源认证提供了新方案和新手段。杨总的黄龙玉防伪溯源革新之路实现了品牌承诺的深化以及消费者权益保护的升级，为消费者和企业之间搭建了一座信任的桥梁。本案例旨在帮助使用者对了解区块链技术，深入思考区块链在具体产品中的应用方法，以实现区块链技术与供应链管理领域的深度融合以及企业的数字化转型和智能化管理。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study recounts how Mr. Yang, the General Manager of Yunnan Benda Huanglong Jade Cultural Communication Co., Ltd., leveraged academia-industry collaboration to integrate blockchain technology into the production, processing, and sale of Huanglong Jade, addressing a trust crisis in the jade market. Partnering with Professor Hu’s team, the initiative employed a blockchain-based digital certificate generation method, creating a complete logical chain encompassing &quot;traceability information recording-enterprise source certification-physical correspondence of certificates.&quot; This approach enabled the Huanglong Jade products to achieve &quot;traceability&quot; and &quot;authenticity verification.&quot; Additionally, Mr. Yang and Professor Hu’ steam jointly developed a blockchain-based anti-counterfeiting and traceability system specifically for Huanglong Jade, effectively applying the method in practice. This system marked a breakthrough in deploying blockchain technology, offering a novel solution and innovative tools for secure, reliable, and cost-effective quality traceability and source authentication in the jade industry. Mr. Yang’s journey of innovation in Huanglong Jade traceability and anti-counterfeiting has enhanced brand credibility and upgraded consumer rights protection, bridging the trust gap between consumers and enterprises. This case aims to deepen understanding of blockchain technology, foster critical thinking on its application in specific products, and facilitate the integration of blockchain with supply chain management to achieve digital transformation and intelligent management for enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《信息系统与信息管理》、《电子商务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">消费者信任理论；创造共享价值理论；创新扩散理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
